Title: Guanxi vs networking: Distinctive configurations of affect- and cognition-based trust in the networks of Chinese vs American managers
Pages: 490-508
Author-Name: Roy Y J Chua
Author-Workplace-Name: Harvard Business School, Boston, USA
Author-Name: Michael W Morris
Author-Workplace-Name: Columbia University, Columbia Business School, New York, USA
Author-Name: Paul Ingram
