Title: Merging without alienating: interventions promoting cross-cultural organizational integration and their limitations
Pages: 468-489
Author-Name: Mary Yoko Brannen
Author-Workplace-Name:  [1] San Jos&eacute; State University, San Jose, USA [2] INSEAD, Fontainebleau, France
Author-Name: Mark F Peterson
Author-Workplace-Name: Florida Atlantic University, Boca Raton, USA
