Title: The role of international assignees&apos; social capital in creating inter-unit intellectual capital: A cross-level model
Pages: 509-526
Author-Name: B Sebastian Reiche
Author-Workplace-Name: IESE Business School, Barcelona, Spain
Author-Name: Anne-Wil Harzing
Author-Workplace-Name: Department of Management and Marketing, University of Melbourne, Melbourne, Australia
Author-Name: Maria L Kraimer
